name: Archetype - Chapter 3 Dawn of Destiny - Robusto
additionalNotes: The Archetype Chapter 3 Dawn of Destiny is a medium-strength cigar that is handmade in the Dominican Republic. It was created as collaboration between Ventura Cigars and master blender Ernesto Perez-Carrillo Jr. The Chapter 3 Dawn of Destiny features an Ecuadorian wrapper with a binder and filler made of premium Nicaraguan tobaccos. The Archetype Chapter 3 Dawn of Destiny has earthy notes with hints cedar and spice.
